25
00:01:33,740 --> 00:01:36,410
This is a laundromat and I'm the owner! Why do you do this all the time?

26
00:01:36,410 --> 00:01:39,250
- So what then?
- Should we call the police?

27
00:01:39,250 --> 00:01:42,240
You villains probably reported me first, didn't you?

28
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:44,270
What on earth is wrong with you?

29
00:01:44,270 --> 00:01:47,000
You're the one who's standing in front of our storefront and prohibiting us from walking downstairs.

30
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,300
You're committing a crime and we can sue you. You know that, right?

31
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:52,220
- You...
- Exactly.
- You're not allowing us to do our business.

32
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,980
Yuki, what are you doing?

33
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:11,410
It's not a big deal. If we just clean a little, it'll be fine.

34
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,870
Can you grab a dustpan for me?

35
00:02:38,180 --> 00:02:40,930
- I can take care of this.
- Thank you.

36
00:02:46,230 --> 00:02:49,440
Mr. Jian, are you okay?

37
00:02:51,550 --> 00:02:55,390
I'm fine. I'm sorry you had to hear all that.

38
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:03,340
Hey, Yuki, is everything all right?

39
00:03:04,130 --> 00:03:06,960
Some customers must have drunkenly knocked over the trash yesterday.

40
