In order to set the tone and foreshadow for the next season, they just ended it right there.

47
00:04:21,420 --> 00:04:24,030
That was so crappy!

48
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:28,270
I agree. Maybe it would be better to get rid of our subscription.

49
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:35,560
No, I don't think so. You would be bored, then.

50
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:38,200
No, I don't think so.

51
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,300
Then, why haven't you gotten rid of your subscription?

52
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:47,310
Oh, I see. It's because of me.

53
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:49,150
No, it's not.

54
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:55,330
I know that you're so good to me.

55
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:03,900
This is getting empty.

56
